data.title: Surname List A
data.meta_description: A list of surnames of ancestors of Polish ethnicity or those who lived in Poland - occupied territories or present-day boundaries.  This includes any ancestors of Lithuanian, Ruthenian, Ukrainian, or German ethnicity living in the former Russian-Poland, German-Poland, Austrian-Poland, Galicia, Silesia, East/West Prussia, etc.  Surnames A-B.
